      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent peer review of model setup by a second analyst not involved in primary model development; checklist-based QC covering boundary conditions, material assignment, and contact definitions.",
      "rationale": "A second credentialed FEA analyst independently reviewed boundary condition application, material property assignments, and contact pair definitions against the ASTM F1717 test setup drawings. No discrepancies identified. Gradation 2 achieved."
