      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from lot-specific tensile coupon data for each test lot; geometric inputs from CMM measurements of actual test specimens; uncertainty in inputs propagated via Monte Carlo (N=1000).",
      "rationale": "Lot-specific tensile coupons (n=3 per lot) provided E, yield strength, and UTS for each test batch. CMM measurements captured as-manufactured geometry deviations. Monte Carlo propagation showed QoI 95th-percentile uncertainty band of ±4.2%, within acceptance bounds. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
