      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA model inputs (geometry, material, boundary conditions) demonstrably equivalent to test specimen inputs within stated uncertainty bounds; equivalency documented in a traceability matrix.",
      "rationale": "Traceability matrix maps each FEA input parameter to its experimental counterpart. CMM geometry, lot coupon material data, and load application point coordinates all confirmed equivalent. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
